            to handle it. That experience means fewer delays and better results."
          </blockquote>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-default dark:text-white">Production Engineer</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-slate-400">Major Operator</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

